snippet.title: Super Mario: The Lost Dreams - Release Trailer [DOWNLOAD][UPDATED 24/8/20]
snippet.description:
UPDATED VERSION 1.2 (24/8/20)

It's finally here, and it's not "the missing memories" anymore.
Super Mario The Lost Dreams is a 50 Star Semi-major hack that features whole new levels and challenges. Find out why Mario seems to be in a strange land with all his recent memories gone...

Download BPS patch: http://www.mediafire.com/file/0m57o8xjk0sqa7v
Download Flips Patcher: https://dl.smwcentral.net/11474/floating.zip

Enjoy!

Music used: Zero Project - Memories of the moon
